description: Display JMX statistics collected using JMXTrans

targets.query: SELECT mean("used"), mean("committed") FROM "jvmMemory" WHERE "hostname" =~ /^$JVM$/ AND "attributeName" = 'HeapMemoryUsage' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "attributeName" fill(null)
